  "original_title": "\u0b9a\u0b9c\u0bbf\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bc8  \u0baa\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0ba4\u0bae\u0bb0\u0bbe\u0b95 \u0b8f\u0bb1\u0bcd\u0bb1\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bca\u0bb3\u0bcd\u0bb3 \u0bb8\u0bcd\u0bb0\u0bc0\u0bb2\u0b99\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bbe \u0baa\u0bca\u0ba4\u0bc1\u0b9c\u0ba9\u0baa\u0bc6\u0bb0\u0bae\u0bc1\u0ba9 \u0ba4\u0baf\u0bbe\u0bb0\u0bcd -  \u0b9c\u0bbf.\u0b8e\u0bb2\u0bcd.\u0baa\u0bc0\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0bb8\u0bcd",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Sri Lanka Podujanaperam is ready to accept Sajith as Prime Minister - GL Peiris",
      "author": "T. Saranya",
      "body_lines": [
        "Sri Lanka Podujanaperamuna is ready to accept Sajith Premadasa as the Prime Minister, said the party's leader Professor G. L. Peiris.",
        "He said that the expectation of the people is to find a solution to the major problems by joining the two parties.",
        "He noted that many members of parliament are ready to support the Dulles unit."
      ],
